🔹 🎯 Task 1: Simple Username Cleaner

You are building a very basic username formatter.

📥 Input:
String username;

⚙️ Requirements:
Remove leading and trailing spaces
Convert the username to lowercase
Print the cleaned username

📤 Output:
Cleaned username: john_doe

📌 Example:
Input: "  John_Doe  "
Output: Cleaned username: john_doe

