🔹 🎯 Task 2: Palindrome Checker (ignore case and spaces)

📥 Input:
String text;

⚙️ Requirements:
Remove all spaces from the text
Ignore uppercase/lowercase differences
Check if the cleaned text reads the same forwards and backwards
Print whether it is a palindrome or not

📤 Output:
"Palindrome" or "Not a palindrome"

📌 Examples:
Input: "Race Car"
Output: Palindrome

Input: "Hello World"
Output: Not a palindrome

