🔹 🎯 Task 3: Mask Email Address

You are building a privacy tool that partially hides an email address.

📥 Input:
String email;

⚙️ Requirements:
Split the email into the part before @ and the part after @
Keep the first and last character of the name part, replace everything in between with ***
Combine it back with the domain part
If the name part has 2 or fewer characters, don't mask it

📤 Output:
Masked email: j***e@gmail.com

📌 Examples:
Input: "johndoe@gmail.com"
Output: Masked email: j***e@gmail.com

Input: "ab@mail.com"
Output: Masked email: ab@mail.com

