🔹 🎯 Task 4: Count Vowels and Consonants

📥 Input:
String sentence;

⚙️ Requirements:
Count all vowels (a, e, i, o, u) in the string (ignore case)
Count all consonants (letters that are not vowels) in the string
Ignore digits, spaces, and special characters — only count letters
Print both counts

📤 Output:
Vowels: X
Consonants: Y

📌 Example:
Input: "Hello World 123!"
Output:
Vowels: 3
Consonants: 7

