🔹 🎯 Task 5: Reverse Words but Keep Order

📥 Input:
String sentence;

⚙️ Requirements:
Split the sentence into words
Reverse each word individually (not the order of words)
Join them back together with a single space
Handle extra spaces between words — output should have only single spaces

📤 Output:
Reversed words: <result>

📌 Examples:
Input: "Hello World"
Output: Reversed words: olleH dlroW

Input: "Java  is   fun"
Output: Reversed words: avaJ si nuf

