🔹 🎯 Task 6: Compress a String (Run-Length Encoding)

📥 Input:
String text;

⚙️ Requirements:
Replace consecutive repeated characters with the character followed by the count
If a character appears only once, just keep the character (no count)
The input will only contain lowercase letters

📤 Output:
Compressed: <result>

📌 Examples:
Input: "aaabbbcc"
Output: Compressed: a3b3c2

Input: "abcd"
Output: Compressed: abcd

Input: "aabcccdddd"
Output: Compressed: a2bc3d4